name: 50on800x80 (black)
description:
The official site for the ‘We need more weird resolution art’ event,  https://800x80.art/ automatically grabbed the 800x80 artworks from Twitter on the hashtag #800x80 and organized them in a smooth feed with credit to the artists.
The Hansup contribution could be no other then the 50 characters I used so many times in animations since 2000. (Black and white version)
